sample_data.py
Generates a realistic corpus of student assignment texts with:
  - Unique original content per student
  - Intentionally shared/copied paragraphs (plagiarism)
  - Technical definitions repeated across multiple students
  - Some verbatim copy-paste, some lightly paraphrased
"""

